# Implementation Plan - Admin Dashboard & Log In Modal Updates

This plan details the steps to implement the changes requested for the EcoPoints Admin Dashboard and Log In Modal, focusing on UI/UX improvements, logic updates, and role management.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database/Schema Changes**: The addition of "Technician" role and updates to User/Admin structure might require backend schema updates (not fully visible in client folder). We will assume mock data or existing API flexibility for now.
> **Asset Requirements**: "EcoPoints Primary Logo (Light version).png" and "Logo Elements (Light)" need to be available in the assets folder.

## Proposed Changes

### Data Layer
#### [MODIFY] [mockData.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/src/data/mockData.js)
- Implement data generators for:
    - **Users**: ~180 Regular Users (Students, Faculty, Staff).
    - **Admins**: ~20 Admin Users (Head Admin, Auditor, Inventory Officer, Technician).
    - **Machines**: 5-10 RVMs linked to LOC-001.
    - **Rewards**: 10-15 Reward Items.
    - **Logs**:
        - `BOTTLE_LOGS`: Generated based on Users and Machines.
        - `MACHINE_LOGS`: Generated based on Machines and Technicians.
        - `ADMIN_LOGS`: Generated based on Admin actions.

### UI Layer
#### [MODIFY] [admin/page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/page.js)
- Update `recentTransactions` to pull from the centralized `BOTTLE_LOGS`.
- Ensure stats cards calculate from the centralized data arrays.

### User Management

#### [MODIFY] [admin/users/page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/users/page.js)
- **Table**:
    - Update pagination text ("Showing X to Y of Z users").
    - Split Username and User ID columns.
    - Add "School" filter.
- Update `recentTransactions` to pull from the centralized `BOTTLE_LOGS`.
- Ensure stats cards calculate from the centralized data arrays.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/logs/bottles/page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/logs/bottles/page.js)
- Replace local empty array return with import of `BOTTLE_LOGS`.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/logs/machines/page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/logs/machines/page.js)
- Replace local empty array return with import of `MACHINE_LOGS`.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/logs/access/page.js](file:///c:/Users/ARCDO%20HP/Documents/GitHub/eco-points/client/app/admin/logs/access/page.js)
- Replace local empty array return with import of `ADMIN_LOGS`.

## Verification Plan
1. **Check Dashboard**: Verify stats match the generated counts (e.g., ~200 users).
2. **Check Logs**: Verify Bottle, Machine, and Admin logs are populated and consistent with the user list.
3. **Check Login**: Verify demo accounts work and log into the correct roles for Arellano University.
